      *OET do file
*By Phil Tian
*version 11.2

clear all

cd E:/

capture log close
log using "OET_log", replace
use oetaug2010_pitstoplevel_v8.dta, clear

gen double ps=psexpectation/1000
drop if winpc==0

program define OET_ML
args lnf sigma alpha beta
tempvar j
gen double `j'=exp(-`beta'*(-ln(winpc))^`alpha')
quietly replace `lnf'=ln(normalden(($ML_y1-`j')/`sigma'))-ln(`sigma')
end

ml model lf OET_ML (sigma:ps=) (alpha:) (beta:)
ml check
ml search
ml maximize, difficult
ml graph
estimates store m1, title (Spec 1-a)


esttab m1 using sesst2.tex, cells("b(star fmt(3)) se") legend  title(MLE result)   nogaps compress replace
